            <lg xml:id="TK1217">
<l>naṉaviṉā ṉalkāk koṭiyār kaṉaviṉāṉ </l>
<l> eṉṉemmaip pīḻip patu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The cruel one who would not favour me in my wakefulness, what right has he to torture me in my dreams?</l>
